'''杜鲁学院'''（Touro College）<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://edu.qq.com/a/20100708/000325_1.htm |title=“野鸡大学”四大特征 根据人生经历颁发学位 |access-date=2014-10-10 |archive-date=2019-12-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191202103741/https://edu.qq.com/a/20100708/000325_1.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>是一所总部位于美国[[纽约|纽约]]的[[私立大学|私立大学]]及同名大学系统，1970年建立，主要服务于[[犹太人|犹太人]]社区<ref name="Bernard">{{cite web |url=http://www.nytimes.com/2010/02/15/nyregion/15lander.html |title=Rabbi Bernard Lander, the Founder of Touro College, Is Dead at 94 |author=Margalit Fox |year=2010 |work= |publisher=New York Times |accessdate=February 19, 2013 |archive-date=2020-06-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200622080255/https://www.nytimes.com/2010/02/15/nyregion/15lander.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，如今全大学系统内有1万9千名学生<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.touro.edu/general/about.asp |title=Official enrollment figures |publisher=Touro.edu |date=June 15, 2011 |accessdate=October 25, 2011 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20111027002041/http://www.touro.edu/general/about.asp |archivedate=2011年10月27日 }}</ref>。

该大学系统中包括数校，位于纽约的同名该校与[[纽约医学院|纽约医学院]]由{{link-en| 中部各州高等教育委员会|Middle States Commission on Higher Education}}认证<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.msche.org/institutions_view.asp?idinstitution=472 |title=Touro College [Accredited] |author= |year=2013 |work= |publisher=Middle States Commission on Higher Education |accessdate=March 5, 2013 |archive-date=2017-06-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170609235759/http://www.msche.org/institutions_view.asp?idinstitution=472 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.msche.org/institutions_view.asp?idinstitution=329 |title=New York Medical College [Accredited] |author= |year=2013 |work= |publisher=Middle States Commission on Higher Education |accessdate=March 5, 2013 |archive-date=2018-04-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180430031754/http://www.msche.org/institutions_view.asp?idinstitution=329 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，
而[[加利福尼亞杜魯大學|加利福尼亞杜魯大學]]和{{link-en|杜鲁内华达大学|Touro University Nevada}}是由[[西部学校学院联合会|西部学校学院联合会]]认证的。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://directory.wascsenior.org/touro-university-california#zoom=15&lat=38.08522&lon=-122.26481&layers=TF0BT |title=Statement of Accreditation Status Touro University California |publisher=Western Association of Schools and Colleges Accrediting Commission for Senior Colleges and Universities |year=2012 |accessdate=March 5, 2013 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130212150253/http://directory.wascsenior.org/touro-university-california#zoom=15&lat=38.08522&lon=-122.26481&layers=TF0BT |archivedate=2013年2月12日 }}</ref>
系统内还包括一所在线网校，名为杜鲁全球大学。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.onlinebusinessdegree.org/2013/01/07/what-degree-gives-business-grads-a-competitive-edge/ |title=存档副本 |access-date=2014-10-10 |archive-date=2020-02-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200202040045/https://www.onlinebusinessdegree.org/2013/01/07/what-degree-gives-business-grads-a-competitive-edge/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>
学院在《[[美国新闻与世界报道|美国新闻与世界报道]]》里属于北方地区排名不公布的层次。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://colleges.usnews.rankingsandreviews.com/best-colleges/touro-college-196592/overall-rankings |title=U.S. News Best Colleges Rankings |access-date=2014-10-10 |archive-date=2013-01-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130106223936/http://colleges.usnews.rankingsandreviews.com/best-colleges/touro-college-196592/overall-rankings |dead-url=no }}</ref>

